<view class="page">
  <view class="page-title">登录玩伴空间</view>
  <view class="page-subtitle">本地开发阶段使用 mockOpenid 登录，后续可切换为真实微信授权。</view>

  <view class="section card stack">
    <view class="login-illustration">一起出发</view>
    <view class="muted">点击后会调用 /api/auth/wx-login 获取 token，并继续请求 /api/users/me 验证当前用户。</view>
    <t-button theme="primary" block loading="{{loading}}" bind:tap="handleLogin">微信授权登录</t-button>
    <t-button variant="text" block bind:tap="goBack">暂不登录</t-button>
  </view>
</view>
